                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18340904-51-off279 t18340904-51-crimeloc282"></join> - on the 14th of August, I saw the prisoner put his hand thirteen or fourteen inches into the shop, and take out a pair of shoes - I ran after him - he was taken, and threw the shoes down, but I did not see him - I am sure he took them.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18340904-51-person369">
