             (police-constable K 138). I took the prisoner, and have the shoes.</p>
               <p>Prisoner's Defence. He came and struck me in the mouth, and said I had taken the shoes - I said I had not, and he began to kick me, and jump upon me - these shoes, as he calls them, were brought after me, but they are boots.</p>
